OL,3,CWording of proposed assisted dying law
OL,4,Con Isle of Man debated
OL,6,FPatients wanting to use a proposed
OL,7,Fassisted dying law on the Isle of Man
OL,8,Fwould have to take life-ending
OL,9,Fmedications themselves rather than
OL,10,Fbeing administered by a doctor, after
OL,11,Fa vote in the island's parliament.
OL,13,FThe wording of the Assisted Dying Bill
OL,14,Fwas being debated on Tuesday, on the
OL,15,Fthird day of its clauses stage.
