OL,3,CWording of proposed assisted dying law
OL,4,Con Isle of Man debated
OL,6,FThe Member of the House of Keys (MHK)
OL,7,Fbehind the Bill said removing the
OL,8,Fability to request physician-
OL,9,Fadministered assisted dying was a
OL,10,F"major change", with patients expected
OL,11,Fto self-administer the necessary
OL,12,Fmedications should the law come into
OL,13,Feffect.
