OL,3,CWording of proposed assisted dying law
OL,4,Con Isle of Man debated
OL,6,FDr Alex Allinson said: "The House of
OL,7,FKeys today approved another key clause
OL,8,Fin a Bill designed to allow for
OL,9,Fchoice, autonomy and dignity for those
OL,10,Fadult island residents with a terminal
OL,11,Fillness, expected to die within 12
OL,12,Fmonths who have a settled intention to
OL,13,Fend their own life.
OL,15,F"Amendments were overwhelmingly agreed
OL,16,Fto provide for self-administration of
OL,17,Fmedications to align this legislation
OL,18,Fwith that already operating around the
OL,19,Fworld where a considerable evidence
OL,20,Fbase exists for how to provide for an
OL,21,Fassisted death."
